name: Tonic GABA Synaptic Transmission in SNr Electrophysiology recordings
citation: Simmons, DeNard (2024) Tonic GABA Synaptic Transmission in SNr Electrophysiology recordings (Version draft) [Data set]. DANDI archive. https://dandiarchive.org/dandiset/001036/draft
description: Ex-vivo mouse brain slice electrophysiological recordings from. SNr neurons. The experiments were performed to discern the source of tonic GABA signal. observed upon SNr neourons that was modulated by D2 class receptor agonist quinpirole.
